OL,3,C'It's kept millions of people alive':
OL,4,CBob Geldof addresses Band Aid criticism
OL,6,FThe release of the 40th anniversary
OL,7,FBand Aid single has not come without
OL,8,Fcontroversy, as ITV News' Arts Editor
OL,9,FNina Nannar reports
OL,11,FSir Bob Geldof is exhausted. He tells
OL,12,Fme that he fell asleep before our
OL,13,Finterview and hence he's a bit late.
OL,15,FBut get him on the subject of Band Aid
OL,16,F2024 and that famous urgency demanding
OL,17,Fyour attention is evident.
