OL,3,C'It's kept millions of people alive':
OL,4,CBob Geldof addresses Band Aid criticism
OL,6,FAs he lists all the vocal
OL,7,Fcollaborations producer Trevor Horn
OL,8,Fhas mixed, from three previous
OL,9,Fversions of the original single, he is
OL,10,Fliterally stamping his feet with
OL,11,Fenthusiasm.
OL,13,FIt's so beautiful he declares, as he
OL,14,Flists all the A-listers who can be
OL,15,Fheard on the new single.
OL,17,FDo They Know It's Christmas is out
OL,18,Fchasing the top spot in the charts
OL,19,Fthis festive season as it marks its
OL,20,F40th anniversary.
