OL,3,C'It's kept millions of people alive':
OL,4,CBob Geldof addresses Band Aid criticism
OL,6,FIn 1984, the original mix raised #8
OL,7,Fmillion for famine relief, and the
OL,8,Ftrust set up afterwards has raised
OL,9,Faround #150 million.
OL,11,FThe record makes money every year, Sir
OL,12,FBob tells me, listing all the ways
OL,13,Fthat has happened. He knows his stuff,
OL,14,Fand is clearly tired of hearing
OL,15,Fcriticism that he doesn't.
OL,17,FClaims that the song perpetuates
OL,18,Fstereotypes about African victims
OL,19,Frelying on Western intervention from
OL,20,Fso-called white saviours have
OL,21,Fintensified over the years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
