OL,3,C'It's kept millions of people alive':
OL,4,CBob Geldof addresses Band Aid criticism
OL,6,FThis year, Ed Sheeran said he wasn't
OL,7,Fasked if he wanted to be included in
OL,8,Fthe 2024 remix and he would have said
OL,9,Fno.
OL,11,FSir Bob has nothing but praise for
OL,12,FSheeran but says they should agree to
OL,13,Fdisagree.
OL,15,FHe says he cannot understand the
OL,16,Fobjections though he welcomes the
OL,17,Freaction that the Band Aid project
OL,18,Fcontinues to get, both positive and
OL,19,Fnegative.
