OL,3,C'It's kept millions of people alive':
OL,4,CBob Geldof addresses Band Aid criticism
OL,6,FHundreds of thousands, perhaps
OL,7,Fmillions, he says, have been helped by
OL,8,Fthe single, which negates all the
OL,9,Fcriticism.
OL,11,FHe believes the end justifies the
OL,12,Fmeans, others may never agree but Sir
OL,13,FBob has his eye on the prize - and
OL,14,Fthat is simply raising money to help
OL,15,Fpeople in Africa through a song
OL,16,Fhastily created four decades ago, but
OL,17,Fwhich has arguably had one of the
OL,18,Fbiggest impacts on popular culture.
